						<p><div class="item">
<h2><a class="listing" style="link" href="/en/Dossiers/CTA-and-S-T/Developments/Commission-and-UN-strengthen-global-environmental-partnership" title="Commission and UN strengthen global environmental partnership" alt="link">Commission and UN strengthen global environmental partnership</a></h2>

	
					<p> <i>Euractiv, 21 September 2004</i>. The Commission and UNEP have signed a new cooperation agreement to speed up delivery of global environmental policies. The partnership will strengthen collaboration at all levels, and is designed to speed-up the delivery of the commitments made at the 2002 World Summit on Sustainable Development in Johannesburg. Areas selected for cooperation include: assistance to developing countries in reaching environment-related targets, and supporting the implementation of multilateral environmental agreements. Last week, UNEP issued a global call to redouble efforts to assess the quantities of methyl bromide, an ozone-depleting pesticide used to kill pests on export crop shipments.</p>
							<p><span class="date">23/12/2004</span></p>
	<div class="cnt">
