						<p><div class="item">
<h2><a class="listing" style="link" href="/en/Dossiers/CTA-and-S-T/Developments/Science-writing-network-launched-in-Malawi" title="Science writing network launched in Malawi" alt="link">Science writing network launched in Malawi</a></h2>

	
					<p> <i>SciDev, 13 August 2004</i>. Malawian journalists have launched a network to promote home-grown science reporting, which they see as central to their country's socio-economic development. The Coalition of Journalists on Environment and Agriculture (COJEA) has been created to help fill a widening gap in Malawian journalism. COJEA will make training available to journalists in science-related aspects of some of the country's key development issues.</p>
							<p><span class="date">23/12/2004</span></p>
	<div class="cnt">
